			              <span class="calc__text--desc">Calculate what you need on your exam to to pass the course.</span>
			          </div></a>
		    	</td>
		    	<td class="calc-container"><a class="calc-link" href="https://itunes.apple.com/ca/app/percentage-calculator-by-math/id1141583865">
		            <div class="calc__img-container"><img class="calc__img" src="img/pc-logo.png" alt="percentage calculator logo" width="88" height="88"></div>
		              <div class="calc__text">
