			            <span class="calc__text--title">Hashtag Everything (Android)</span>
			            <span class="calc__text--desc">Literally hashtag EVERYTHING with ease.</span>
			        </div></a>
		        </td>
		        
		    </tr>
		    <tr>
		    	<td class="calc-container"><a class="calc-link" href="https://itunes.apple.com/ca/app/doge-bounce/id850547912?mt=8">
